---
---

<section id="projects" class="section">
  <p class="section-label">Projects</p>
  <h2 class="section-heading">What I've built.</h2>

  <div class="project-list">

    <div class="project-card cmyk-border-subtle">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h3 class="project-name">Mini Mealie</h3>
        <span class="project-badge">Chrome &amp; Firefox</span>
      </div>
      <p class="project-desc">Open-source browser extension with 2,000+ active users and growing international adoption. Built with AI-assisted workflows and custom MCP tools. Cross-browser Firefox support added via community collaboration.</p>
      <span class="project-stack">TypeScript &middot; MCP</span>
    </div>

    <div class="project-card cmyk-border-subtle">
      <div class="project-header">
        <h3 class="project-name">Self-Hosted Infrastructure</h3>
        <span class="project-badge">Home Lab</span>
      </div>
      <p class="project-desc">30+ container home lab running local LLMs (Ollama) and AI agent frameworks (Mastra) behind zero-trust architecture: Authelia SSO, Traefik reverse proxy, Cloudflare Tunnel, CrowdSec IPS.</p>
      <span class="project-stack">Docker &middot; Ollama &middot; Mastra &middot; Traefik &middot; Cloudflare &middot; CrowdSec</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .project-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .project-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 8px;
    filter: saturate(0%);
    transition: filter 0.5s ease;
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    filter: saturate(100%);
  }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .project-name {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .project-badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .project-desc {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .project-stack {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }
</style>
